# Specialized Agent Context Files

This directory contains detailed context documents for specialized development agents:

- `architecture-context.md` - System design, database schema, service boundaries
- `graphql-context.md` - GraphQL schema design, mutations, queries, resolvers
- `rails-context.md` - Rails 8 conventions, Hotwire, ActiveRecord patterns
- `testing-context.md` - RSpec patterns, factories, VCR, system tests
- `reviewer-context.md` - Code review checklist, quality standards, security

These files will be created as needed during development.
